parameters.name: Hour
parameters.description: Hour of the day in Universal time (to 4 decimal places).

parameters.name: BE_ENR
parameters.description: East component of the magnetic field in ENR coordinates.

parameters.name: BN_ENR
parameters.description: North component of the magnetic field in ENR coordinates.

parameters.name: BR_ENR
parameters.description: Radial component of the magnetic field in ENR coordinates.

parameters.name: Bx_SG
parameters.description: X component of the magnetic field in SG coordinates.

parameters.name: By_SG
parameters.description: Y component of the magnetic field in SG coordinates.

parameters.name: Bz_SG
parameters.description: Z component of the magnetic field in SG coordinates.

parameters.name: Latitude
parameters.description: Lunar Latitude in degrees; north is positive.

parameters.name: Altitude
parameters.description: Approximate altitude of spacecraft in kilometers.
